- Use firebase functions V2
- Use Firebase Authentication with custom claims (e.g. userType) for enhanced user management and security
- Implement Firestore for real-time data synchronization
- Utilize Firebase Storage for file uploads and management
- Implement proper error handling and offline support using Firebase SDK
